name: ROOTS
description:
This is my genesis.
The tree in the picture grows against any probability on a balcony of a building destroyed by time in Old Havana, Cuba. 
The dichotomy between its branches looking for the sky, but clinging its roots to the home where it was born is a message of hope, for everyone who was a seed and it's finding his own shining light.
Search for your own path to grow no matter what, more can always be achieved.
The number of editions it's my actual age, 27.
